name: Flextein™ SEA2010
description: Flextein™ SEA2010 is a two-component thermally conductive RTV silicone sealant for insulating and protecting electrical and electronic components from application and environmental stresses. This rubber-like compound resists shock and vibration, intended for exclusion of moisture and corrosive agents. High conductivity makes FlexteinTM SEA2007 suitable for electronic components or packaging requiring heat dissipation while sealed.
